## 5. Local JSON Adapter

Create:

```text
src/engine/benchmarks/sources/localJsonBenchmarkSourceAdapter.ts
```

Purpose:
- import a JSON benchmark definition from disk

Flow:
- read file
- parse JSON
- normalize if already correct shape
- attach source metadata
- validate
- return result

